# VPC Traffic Flow and Security

## Project Overview

This project focused on controlling and securing network traffic within an Amazon Virtual Private Cloud (VPC). I configured route tables, Security Groups, and Network ACLs to understand how AWS evaluates traffic at both the instance and subnet levels.

By implementing multiple layers of network security, I reinforced the AWS Shared Responsibility Model and gained practical experience designing secure cloud networking architectures.

